                                </ol>
                                <p style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:.5in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;text-align:justify;'><span style='font-size:16px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'>The Website allows users to solicit offers to buy or sell Digital Assets.</span></p>
                                <p style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:.5in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;text-align:justify;'><span style='font-size:16px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'>When a user initiates a transaction for the purchase or sale of Digital Assets, the transaction is consummated pursuant to this Agreement and to the additional terms, if any, detailed by the user or the user&rsquo;s counterparty. A step-by-step guide on buying and selling Digital Assets on the Crypto Street Market Marketplace can be found at&nbsp;</span><a href="https://cryptostreetmarket.com" target="_blank"><span style='font-size:16px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#0B70D5;'>https://Crypto Street Market.com/support/en-us/categories/360000409494-How-to-Buy-and-Sell</span></a><span style='font-size:16px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'>.</span></p>
